name: Wisecrack
infos: Wisecrack is one of two popular 5.7s at Burger and Fries.  Begin left of Carch Me, and right of the gentle ramp, Dusty Eyes.    Climb some left angling cracks to a small tree stump halfway up the face.  Move right to a flake, and layback unttil making a few easier moves to the top.        The initial moves into the flake are disconcerting and the gear is small.-Gear to 2".  #3 microcams protect the inital moves onto the flake.
